## ðŸ§  Memory Allocation (1 Occurrence)

```c
#include <mpi.h>
#include <stdio.h>
#include <stdlib.h>

int main(int argc, char *argv[]) {
    MPI_Init(&argc, &argv);

    int *buf;
    buf = (int *)malloc(100 * sizeof(int)); // memory for point-to-point send/recv

    MPI_Finalize();
    return 0;
}
